data.description: Step into this inviting two-story colonial residence situated in a fantastic neighborhood! This home offers an impressive array of features, including 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, a 2-car garage, a finished basement with storage which also includes plumbing rough-in, and an enchanting landscaped lot. The kitchen has been tastefully updated with gleaming granite countertops, setting the stage for culinary delights.  As you navigate the main level, the ambiance is elevated by the presence of beautiful hardwood floors and a cozy fireplace, creating an ideal setting for both daily living and entertaining guests. The upper level hosts four spacious bedrooms, providing ample space for relaxation.  One of the highlights of this property is the expansive deck, paved basketball court, open space, and perfect for enjoying your mornings or evenings in a serene outdoor setting. The carefully landscaped lot adds to the visual appeal and charm of this wonderful home.  Located in Marlton, this residence not only offers a delightful living space but also provides convenient access to D.C., Southern Maryland, and the Annapolis/Baltimore area. Commuting and exploring the nearby regions become effortless from this strategic location. Come see for yourself before it's too late!
